{"parentUuid":"5b5412b6-dded-4975-af6c-41184bd25974","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"bab18d11-a54d-4359-a1e4-66e491360a7c","agentId":"a18902932a394df42","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CBA9V9DGZq1wb8oH5FQbCq","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Meterly\n2\t\n3\tUsage-metering ingestion API. See `PROJECT.md` for the product spec and\n4\t`docs/system_architecture.md` for the implementation overview.\n5\t\n6\t## Quickstart\n7\t\n8\t```bash\n9\tpoetry install\n10\tpoetry run alembic upgrade head\n11\tpoetry run uvicorn src.main:app --port 8000\n12\t```\n13\t\n14\t`GET /health` returns 200 with no dependencies (liveness). `GET /health/ready`\n15\tchecks the database connection and migration head (readiness).\n16\t"}]},"uuid":"0d58b257-61b1-41e5-8e86-018255039fc7","timestamp":"2026-07-11T23:31:19.149Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/README.md","content":"# Meterly\n\nUsage-metering ingestion API. See `PROJECT.md` for the product spec and\n`docs/system_architecture.md` for the implementation overview.\n\n## Quickstart\n\n```bash\npoetry install\npoetry run alembic upgrade head\npoetry run uvicorn src.main:app --port 8000\n```\n\n`GET /health` returns 200 with no dependencies (liveness). `GET /health/ready`\nchecks the database connection and migration head (readiness).\n","numLines":16,"startLine":1,"totalLines":16}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"5b5412b6-dded-4975-af6c-41184bd25974","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usage-daily"}
