oves that class of IDOR parameter entirely.\n\n**Validation boundary discipline:** no schema in this directory ever builds\nSQL or touches the database — every validated field travels onward only as a\nplain Python value (or, for `usage_daily.py`, the `DailyDateWindow` dataclass)\nthat the service/repository layers bind as a query parameter.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"17ee89f8-bcf1-4cce-8a34-380c417888e2","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"8b12bd3f-3c00-43c5-ad29-92ed49e714d3","version":"2.1.207","gitBranch":"feature/usage-daily"}
