{"parentUuid":"7f4b32cd-e503-4c41-91e4-2def33bcdd58","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"a18902932a394df42","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcwAfNKg7VmtJ4y79QeKE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011tZcx4LtuQ2Tcn1qZnc5Er","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/mnt/c/Users/brett/OneDrive/Documents/GitHub/meterly-pipeline-test/docs/system_architecture.md","old_string":"- `usage_rollup` — derived hourly aggregate (migration 0002, expand +\n  backfill from `events`). Composite PK `(api_key_id, customer_id, metric,\n  window_start)`; RLS policy `usage_rollup_tenant_isolation`.","new_string":"- `usage_rollup` — derived hourly aggregate (migration 0002, expand +\n  backfill from `events`). Composite PK `(api_key_id, customer_id, metric,\n  window_start)`; RLS policy `usage_rollup_tenant_isolation`, **`FORCE`d as of\n  migration 0004** (security remediation — the app connects as the table\n  owner `meterly_app`, which otherwise bypasses non-`FORCE` RLS regardless of\n  `NOBYPASSRLS`; mirrors `0003`'s `FORCE` on `quotas`). Read by `GET\n  /v1/usage`, `GET /v1/usage/daily`, and `GET /v1/usage/export`; written by\n  `POST /v1/events`'s rollup increment. **Known gap:** `events` (migration\n  0001) still carries the same non-`FORCE` RLS gap, deliberately out of scope\n  for `0004` — see `.pipeline/pr-description.md`."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1256,"cache_read_input_tokens":109663,"output_tokens":617,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1256},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":617,"cache_read_input_tokens":109663,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1256,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1256,"ephemeral